{"id":168,"ayahs":[{"number":144,"arabic":"قَالَ يَٰمُوسَىٰٓ إِنِّى ٱصْطَفَيْتُكَ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ بِرِسَٰلَٰتِى وَبِكَلَٰمِى فَخُذْ مَآ ءَاتَيْتُكَ وَكُن مِّنَ ٱلشَّٰكِرِينَ","translation":"Said [God]: \"O Moses! Behold, I have raised thee above all people by virtue of the messages which I have entrusted to thee, and by virtue of My speaking [unto thee]: hold fast, therefore, unto what I have vouchsafed thee, and be among the grateful!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1098.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79746,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(আল্লাহ) বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79747,"position":2,"arabic":"يَـٰمُوسَىٰٓ","translation":"\"হে মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79748,"position":3,"arabic":"إِنِّى","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79749,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱصْطَفَيْتُكَ","translation":"তোমাকে আমি বেছে নিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79750,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79751,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79752,"position":7,"arabic":"بِرِسَـٰلَـٰتِى","translation":"দিয়ে আমার রিসালাত (বাণী)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79753,"position":8,"arabic":"وَبِكَلَـٰمِى","translation":"ও দিয়ে আমার বাক্যালাপ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79754,"position":9,"arabic":"فَخُذْ","translation":"অতএব গ্রহণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79755,"position":10,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79756,"position":11,"arabic":"ءَاتَيْتُكَ","translation":"তোমাকে আমি দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79757,"position":12,"arabic":"وَكُن","translation":"এবং হও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79758,"position":13,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79759,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلشَّـٰكِرِينَ","translation":"কৃতজ্ঞদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_144_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79760,"position":15,"arabic":"١٤٤","translation":"(১৪৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":145,"arabic":"وَكَتَبْنَا لَهُۥ فِى ٱلْأَلْوَاحِ مِن كُلِّ شَىْءٍۢ مَّوْعِظَةًۭ وَتَفْصِيلًۭا لِّكُلِّ شَىْءٍۢ فَخُذْهَا بِقُوَّةٍۢ وَأْمُرْ قَوْمَكَ يَأْخُذُوا۟ بِأَحْسَنِهَا ۚ سَأُو۟رِيكُمْ دَارَ ٱلْفَٰسِقِينَ","translation":"And We ordained for him in the tablets [of the Law] all manner of admonition, clearly spelling out everything. And [We said:] \"Hold fast unto them with [all thy] strength, and bid thy people to hold fast to their most goodly rules.\" I will show you the way the iniquitous shall go.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1099.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79870,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَتَبْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা লিখেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79871,"position":2,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"জন্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79872,"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79873,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْأَلْوَاحِ","translation":"ফলকগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79874,"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79875,"position":6,"arabic":"كُلِّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79876,"position":7,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","translation":"জিনিসের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79877,"position":8,"arabic":"مَّوْعِظَةًۭ","translation":"উপদেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79878,"position":9,"arabic":"وَتَفْصِيلًۭا","translation":"ও বিস্তারিত ব্যাখ্যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79879,"position":10,"arabic":"لِّكُلِّ","translation":"জন্যে সব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79880,"position":11,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","translation":"কিছুর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79881,"position":12,"arabic":"فَخُذْهَا","translation":"\"অতএব ধারণ করো তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79882,"position":13,"arabic":"بِقُوَّةٍۢ","translation":"ভাবে দৃঢ়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79883,"position":14,"arabic":"وَأْمُرْ","translation":"এবং নির্দেশ দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79884,"position":15,"arabic":"قَوْمَكَ","translation":"তোমার জাতিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79885,"position":16,"arabic":"يَأْخُذُوا۟","translation":"তারা গ্রহণ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79886,"position":17,"arabic":"بِأَحْسَنِهَا ۚ","translation":"সহ তার উত্তম(তাৎপর্য)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79888,"position":18,"arabic":"سَأُو۟رِيكُمْ","translation":"শীঘ্রই আমি দেখাবো তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79889,"position":19,"arabic":"دَارَ","translation":"বাসস্হান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79890,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلْفَـٰسِقِينَ","translation":"সত্যত্যাগীদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_145_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79891,"position":21,"arabic":"١٤٥","translation":"(১৪৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":146,"arabic":"سَأَصْرِفُ عَنْ ءَايَٰتِىَ ٱلَّذِينَ يَتَكَبَّرُونَ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ بِغَيْرِ ٱلْحَقِّ وَإِن يَرَوْا۟ كُلَّ ءَايَةٍۢ لَّا يُؤْمِنُوا۟ بِهَا وَإِن يَرَوْا۟ سَبِيلَ ٱلرُّشْدِ لَا يَتَّخِذُوهُ سَبِيلًۭا وَإِن يَرَوْا۟ سَبِيلَ ٱلْغَىِّ يَتَّخِذُوهُ سَبِيلًۭا ۚ ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمْ كَذَّبُوا۟ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا وَكَانُوا۟ عَنْهَا غَٰفِلِينَ","translation":"From My messages shall I cause to turn away all those who, without any right, behave haughtily on earth: for, though they may see every sign [of the truth], they do not believe in it, and though they may see the path of rectitude, they do not choose to follow it-whereas, if they see a path of error, they take it for their own: this, because they have given the lie to Our messages, and have remained heedless of them,\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1100.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":79983,"position":1,"arabic":"سَأَصْرِفُ","translation":"অচিরেই ফিরিয়ে দিবো আমি (দৃষ্টি)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79984,"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79985,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِىَ","translation":"আমার নিদর্শনগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79986,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79987,"position":5,"arabic":"يَتَكَبَّرُونَ","translation":"অহংকার করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79988,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79989,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79990,"position":8,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ভাবে নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79991,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقِّ","translation":"ন্যায়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79992,"position":10,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79993,"position":11,"arabic":"يَرَوْا۟","translation":"তারা দেখেও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79994,"position":12,"arabic":"كُلَّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79995,"position":13,"arabic":"ءَايَةٍۢ","translation":"নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79996,"position":14,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79997,"position":15,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُوا۟","translation":"তারা ঈমান আনবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79998,"position":16,"arabic":"بِهَا","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79999,"position":17,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80000,"position":18,"arabic":"يَرَوْا۟","translation":"তারা দেখেও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80001,"position":19,"arabic":"سَبِيلَ","translation":"পথ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80002,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلرُّشْدِ","translation":"সঠিক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80003,"position":21,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80004,"position":22,"arabic":"يَتَّخِذُوهُ","translation":"তারা গ্রহণ করবে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80005,"position":23,"arabic":"سَبِيلًۭا","translation":"পথ হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80006,"position":24,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"কিন্তু যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80007,"position":25,"arabic":"يَرَوْا۟","translation":"তারা দেখে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80008,"position":26,"arabic":"سَبِيلَ","translation":"পথ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80009,"position":27,"arabic":"ٱلْغَىِّ","translation":"ভ্রান্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80010,"position":28,"arabic":"يَتَّخِذُوهُ","translation":"তারা গ্রহণ করবে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80011,"position":29,"arabic":"سَبِيلًۭا ۚ","translation":"পথ হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80013,"position":30,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80014,"position":31,"arabic":"بِأَنَّهُمْ","translation":"এজন্যে যে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80015,"position":32,"arabic":"كَذَّبُوا۟","translation":"মিথ্যারোপ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80016,"position":33,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا","translation":"প্রতি নিদর্শনগুলোর আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80017,"position":34,"arabic":"وَكَانُوا۟","translation":"এবং তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80018,"position":35,"arabic":"عَنْهَا","translation":"সে সব হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80019,"position":36,"arabic":"غَـٰفِلِينَ","translation":"উদাসীন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_146_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80020,"position":37,"arabic":"١٤٦","translation":"(১৪৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":147,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ كَذَّبُوا۟ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا وَلِقَآءِ ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ حَبِطَتْ أَعْمَٰلُهُمْ ۚ هَلْ يُجْزَوْنَ إِلَّا مَا كَانُوا۟ يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"Hence, all who give the lie to Our messages, and [thus] to the truth of the life to come -in vain shall be all their doings: [for] are they to be rewarded for aught but what they were wont to do?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1101.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":80060,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"এবং যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80061,"position":2,"arabic":"كَذَّبُوا۟","translation":"মিথ্যাররোপ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80062,"position":3,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا","translation":"প্রতি নিদর্শনগুলোর আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80063,"position":4,"arabic":"وَلِقَآءِ","translation":"ও সাক্ষাত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80064,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","translation":"আখেরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80065,"position":6,"arabic":"حَبِطَتْ","translation":"নষ্ট হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80066,"position":7,"arabic":"أَعْمَـٰلُهُمْ ۚ","translation":"আমলগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80068,"position":8,"arabic":"هَلْ","translation":"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80069,"position":9,"arabic":"يُجْزَوْنَ","translation":"তাদের পুরষ্কার দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80070,"position":10,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80071,"position":11,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80072,"position":12,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80073,"position":13,"arabic":"يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তারা কাজ করে আসছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_147_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80074,"position":14,"arabic":"١٤٧","translation":"(১৪৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":148,"arabic":"وَٱتَّخَذَ قَوْمُ مُوسَىٰ مِنۢ بَعْدِهِۦ مِنْ حُلِيِّهِمْ عِجْلًۭا جَسَدًۭا لَّهُۥ خُوَارٌ ۚ أَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ أَنَّهُۥ لَا يُكَلِّمُهُمْ وَلَا يَهْدِيهِمْ سَبِيلًا ۘ ٱتَّخَذُوهُ وَكَانُوا۟ ظَٰلِمِينَ","translation":"AND IN his absence the people of Moses took to worshipping the effigy of a calf [made] of their ornaments, which gave forth a lowing sound.\" Did they not see that it could neither speak unto them nor guide them in any way? [And yet] they took to worshipping it, for they were evildoers:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1102.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":80142,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱتَّخَذَ","translation":"এবং বানালো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80143,"position":2,"arabic":"قَوْمُ","translation":"জাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80144,"position":3,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰ","translation":"মূসার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80145,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80146,"position":5,"arabic":"بَعْدِهِۦ","translation":"পর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80147,"position":6,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"দ্বারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80148,"position":7,"arabic":"حُلِيِّهِمْ","translation":"অলংকারগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80149,"position":8,"arabic":"عِجْلًۭا","translation":"বাছুর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80150,"position":9,"arabic":"جَسَدًۭا","translation":"অবয়ব (সম্পন্ন)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80151,"position":10,"arabic":"لَّهُۥ","translation":"ছিলো তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80152,"position":11,"arabic":"خُوَارٌ ۚ","translation":"হাম্বারব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80154,"position":12,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"কি না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80155,"position":13,"arabic":"يَرَوْا۟","translation":"তারা দেখে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_148_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":80156,"position":14,"